# BNI Loyalty — Back Office Portal

Front-end prototype for a banking loyalty program back-office portal. Operations, product, finance, and approval teams manage loyalty points, monitor KPIs, and run reports.

**Branding:** BNI Loyalty — Back Office Portal

## Stack

React 19 · TypeScript 5.8 (strict) · Vite 7 · Tailwind 3.4 · Recharts 2.15 · Lucide React

## Prototype constraints

- Mock data only — no backend, API, or persistence
- No authentication — role toggle is UI-only
- No URL routing — navigation via `useState<RouteKey>` in `src/App.tsx`
- Pages live in `src/App.tsx`; types in `src/types.ts`; data in `src/data/mockData.ts`

